name: Web Work
description:
Made for Minijam 123: Web! You are a spider, ready to eat his dinner, when an angry bumble seems to stumble upon your web. Protect your food and do not mess with the bumblebee!

Tap where you want to go, and just move the mouse around to move your web. You can only move your food (the firefly) with your web. Make sure not to fall off, it`s pretty far from the ground!
